{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>ShadowLess Light</u> is a visual novel with role-playing elements. You can create and customize your character attributes, skills and cybernetic implants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/testt.png?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You write the story by using <u>dice rolls</u> and making decisions, choosing between a stealthy or direct approach. Will you be charming or threatening? Do you want to use your wits or play the fool?\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/Guide-7.gif?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s set in a dystopian <u><strong>Cyberpunk</strong></u> future, where justice is privatized by a megacorporation called ShadowLess Light. You are going to work as one of its agents, a ShadowLess: <u>judge, jury and executioner</u>, all rolled into one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/Guide-8.gif?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features a system of notes and clues to keep track of all the information and gradually uncover the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/Guide-2.gif?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo includes <strong>150,000 words</strong>, <strong>20,000 lines of code</strong>, <strong>900 renders</strong>, <strong>46 songs</strong>, <strong>160 dice rolls</strong>, <strong>250 menus</strong>, and offers over <u><strong>2 hours of gameplay</strong></u>.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3478800?t=1739901969","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739901969","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/3fa55e37997df71eced80ff559ccb70e6ed77f43/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739901969","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/3fa55e37997df71eced80ff559ccb70e6ed77f43/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739901969","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The game touches on sensitive topics, but they are not its main focus. There are criminals, some violence, blood, profanity, sexual references, deaths... But none of this is the core theme of the game, as it revolves around a detective story\u2014catching criminals."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>ShadowLess Light</u> is a visual novel with role-playing elements. You can create and customize your character attributes, skills and cybernetic implants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/testt.png?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You write the story by using <u>dice rolls</u> and making decisions, choosing between a stealthy or direct approach. Will you be charming or threatening? Do you want to use your wits or play the fool?\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/Guide-7.gif?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s set in a dystopian <u><strong>Cyberpunk</strong></u> future, where justice is privatized by a megacorporation called ShadowLess Light. You are going to work as one of its agents, a ShadowLess: <u>judge, jury and executioner</u>, all rolled into one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/Guide-8.gif?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features a system of notes and clues to keep track of all the information and gradually uncover the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/extras/Guide-2.gif?t=1739901969\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo includes <strong>150,000 words</strong>, <strong>20,000 lines of code</strong>, <strong>900 renders</strong>, <strong>46 songs</strong>, <strong>160 dice rolls</strong>, <strong>250 menus</strong>, and offers over <u><strong>2 hours of gameplay</strong></u>.</p>","developers":["Uncommon Role"],"fullgame":{"appid":"3478790","name":"ShadowLess Light"},"genres":[{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478800/header.jpg?t=1739901969","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 16.04+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> 10.6+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257090713,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090713/movie480.mp4?t=1739901967","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090713/movie_max.mp4?t=1739901967"},"name":"ShadowLess Light Demo Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257090713/0c0bb4a97b6717c7aa8114422a8af60af429c6b